56:11.760 --> 56:15.360
# Oh ah, the sound of the men

56:15.360 --> 56:19.160
# They're working on the chain gang

56:19.160 --> 56:21.640
# All day long they're singing

56:21.640 --> 56:27.800
# Mm hoh uh ah

56:29.320 --> 56:33.520
# Mm ah... #

