Diane, look at this rat I found.

57:02.320 --> 57:06.280
Any vermin under ten kilos
are yours, bag it and bin it.

57:06.280 --> 57:07.880
No, it's a graffiti rat.

57:07.880 --> 57:11.400
Council said paint over
any graffiti so crack on.

57:12.680 --> 57:14.640
It's awfully good.

57:14.640 --> 57:17.000
Less debating, more painting.

