57:25.960 --> 57:29.240
# Oh, lord, that's the sound
of the men... #

57:31.200 --> 57:33.400
I knew who it was from page one.

57:33.400 --> 57:34.840
Nothing gets past me.

57:52.040 --> 57:54.280
# The sound of the men

57:54.280 --> 57:58.920
# Working on the chain gang

57:58.920 --> 58:02.440
# Everyday that's the sound of them

58:02.440 --> 58:06.480
# They're working on the chain gang

58:06.480 --> 58:08.600
This is what they're saying!

58:08.600 --> 58:11.440
# I'm going home one of these days

58:11.440 --> 58:14.360
# I'm going home
Yes, I am

58:14.360 --> 58:16.000
# See my woman... #
